 Someone like Ban Sook...

55
00:06:23,420 --> 00:06:26,100
 Will I be able to meet someone like him?

56
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:41,240
 Ban Sook has left.

57
00:07:10,490 --> 00:07:12,050
I didn't order it.

58
00:07:12,050 --> 00:07:14,210
It's a gift.

59
00:07:15,794 --> 00:07:18,628
Thank you, but I won't accept it.

60
00:07:18,628 --> 00:07:20,620
Did you get dumped?

61
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:25,855
I told you to stay away from that one.

62
00:07:25,855 --> 00:07:29,485
I knew it. You're not good at sorting out a nice guy.

63
00:07:29,485 --> 00:07:32,685
Even if I'm really bad at sorting out a nice guy,

64
00:07:32,685 --> 00:07:35,089
I would never meet someone like y...

65
00:07:40,675 --> 00:07:45,105
Do you perhaps still...

66
00:07:45,105 --> 00:07:46,625
What?

67
00:07:46,625 --> 00:07:48,920
Why are you looking at me with those pitiful eyes?

68
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:52,300
Stop it.

69
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:55,625
I've already given up on you.

70
00:07:55,625 --> 00:07:57,540
You...

71
