I've been determined since I first saw you,

74
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:12,440
that I would never date you.

75
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:14,105
Pardon?

76
00:08:14,105 --> 00:08:15,757
Such a decision...

77
00:08:15,757 --> 00:08:17,691
would be opposite normally.

78
00:08:17,691 --> 00:08:19,806
You're a good friend

79
00:08:19,806 --> 00:08:21,486
and a nice person.

80
00:08:21,486 --> 00:08:24,095
So I've decided that I would see you forever.

81
00:08:24,095 --> 00:08:27,000
For that, I would have to stay as a friend of yours.

82
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:29,280
That was my decision.

83
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:34,554
If we date, then there could be some incidents.

84
00:08:34,554 --> 00:08:37,479
And if we break up, then it would be the end of our relationship.

85
00:08:38,629 --> 00:08:40,240
I don't want to take that risk.

86
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:42,620
I want to be good friends with you for good.

87
00:08:42,620 --> 00:08:46,420
So please remain as my friend forever, Ji Seung Heon!

88
00:08:47,585 --> 00:08:52,300
If we date, we could not have a dispute like this.

89
00:08:52,300 --> 00:08:55,810
I'll keep having disputes with you as a friend.

90
00:08:55,810 --> 00:08:58,710
Yes, please.

91
00:08:58,710 --> 00:09:01,695
You tease and bother me...

92
00:09:01,695 --> 00:09:05,210
Please share comforting words when I feel depressed like I do today.

93
00:09:05,210 --> 00:09:06,863
I'll do that for you, too.

94
00:09:06,863 --> 00:09:10,258
Okay, I'll give comfort and encouragement on difficult days, and I'll bother you all the time.

95
00:09:10,258 --> 00:09:13,561
- Go away! 
 - You go away.

96
00:09:13,561 --> 00:09:14,770
I'm leaving for class.

97
00:09:14,770 --> 00:09:18,054
Thank you for the cake. Let's just say I ate it.

98
00:09:32,625 --> 00:09:34,850
How...

99
00:09:37,332 --> 00:09:39,775
Have you decided to give it up?

100
00:09:40,769 --> 00:09:42,474
Yes.

101
00:09:43,073 --> 00:09:47,143
It's your decision, no matter what choice you make.

102
00:09:49,260 --> 00:09:51,520
Then you're going back to the goblin world,

103
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:54,140
and you'll never be able to come back to the human world.

104
00:09:54,140 --> 00:09:56,170
Do you understand?

105
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:03,350
How was it for you, Goblin Queen?

106
00:10:03,900 --> 00:10:05,720
What?

107
00:10:06,340 --> 00:10:09,070
How did you feel when you had to leave someone you loved?

108
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:19,220
I wanted to commit suicide.

109
00:10:19,220 --> 00:10:22,955
It was tough. I regretted it.

110
00:10:23,737 --> 00:10:25,820
If I became human,

111
00:10:25,820 --> 00:10:28,360
I wouldn't be in this much pain.

112
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:30,860
Even if we couldn't recognize each other,

113
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:34,700
we might've encountered and fallen in love with each other by chance.

114
00:10:35,450 --> 00:10:39,730
Even if it wasn't in this lifetime. Maybe in my next life.

115
00:10:39,730 --> 00:10:42,580
Or the next one.

116
00:10:44,260 --> 00:10:47,540
I shouldn't have wanted to become a human,

117
00:10:47,540 --> 00:10:51,465
then everything would have been alright.

118
00:10:56,660 --> 00:11:01,835
The chances are that you cannot meet each other even if you become human.

119
00:11:01,835 --> 00:11:05,040
There's no certainty that you would be his lover even if you meet him.

120
00:11:08,580 --> 00:11:12,040
There's this word in the human world.

121
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:14,120
Fate.

122
00:11:18,070 --> 00:11:21,110
The goblin you're looking for isn't here.

123
00:11:21,110 --> 00:11:23,000
He'll never come back.

124
00:11:23,016 --> 00:11:26,578
I can't sleep at night lately, because I'm so ashamed.

125
00:11:26,578 --> 00:11:30,228
When I think of you and that goblin,

126
00:11:30,228 --> 00:11:33,180
I get outraged.

127
00:11:34,300 --> 00:11:38,020
I think I would be haunted by this emotion forever if I fail to kill that goblin.

128
00:11:38,684 --> 00:11:40,819
Oh...

129
00:11:40,819 --> 00:11:44,655
You have such high self-esteem.

130
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:48,240
That's why I thought...

131
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:51,990
If you and that goblin are in that kind of relationship,

132
00:11:52,740 --> 00:11:55,620
he would've come when you're in danger.

133
00:11:55,620 --> 00:11:59,295
I thought that exorcists weren't allowed to kill humans.

134
00:11:59,295 --> 00:12:01,460
We're not allowed to.

135
00:12:02,740 --> 00:12:06,200
I'll torture you just painfully enough so you won't die.

136
